## Explanation

In the DI4D we worked with figma first to create a natural and intuitive user expierence. 
We made a lofi design first and preformed an analysis of it based on the 10 heuristics of Nielsen, 
after which we made a hifi design. Throughout the process we involved the client to cross check 
our design with the clients needs.

